Page Manager liked on Facebook is a powerful web browser extension that helps users manage lists of pages they like and follow on Facebook. This extension provides a convenient and easy experience in managing activities on Facebook, making it easier for users to browse and interact with the pages.

The page manager liked on Facebook helps users save time and effort in managing and interacting with pages on Facebook. With this extension, users can monitor activity, and find new sites conveniently and efficiently.
